node.text:
Not only has it been a pleasure being blessed with the responsibility of carrying a child but I’m overjoyed that I’m doing it with my best friend @leeksneed . After losing my grandmother, this new blessing has been nothing short of amazing. After every storm there’s a rainbow 🌈👶🏽💙 New blessings, new adventures, new LIFE.  #Partyof3 #BoyMom 
🎥: @hiddenimagesdc

Aye Moe!  
 
Forgot your wallet at home? No issue. Technology is our best friend! We can now use our phones to pay with the @paypal & @venmo apps when we are out shopping at Foot Locker stores nationwide! #FootLockerPartner Just take your phone out at the register, scan and pay! 
 
Get $10 cashback the first you time you spend $50 or more with PayPal or Venmo QR Code at any @footlocker, Inc. store through Oct 31, 2021. Terms Apply.

node.text:
Dear SON🧸,

As i sit here and reflect on the journey in life up unto this point; the obstacles I’ve faced/overcame, the accomplishments I’ve made despite the non believers & statistics from the environment i grew up in… no moment could ever amount up to this moment in life. All i think about is you. I can’t wait to meet you, kiss you & give you every ounce of love i have in my body. You’ve changed me in so many ways, and have given me the greatest role of my lifetime —— a MOTHER. 
I am so grateful of the gifts you’ve given me from the inside; and no matter how hard my day has been, all it takes is for your little feet to start kicking to make everything alright. You may think that I’m your teacher, but, in reality it’s you that’s teaching me. I’m so much better because of you. You fill a place in my heart that i never knew was empty 💙 I’m looking forward too & very excited/nervous for our “blind date” lol a.k.a labor. But until then i love you my sweet boy. See you soon

Love,
Your mom 🤞🏽

📸: @mymanbriscoe 
Makeup: @e.marieglamour 
Hair: @daretohavehair / Styled: @mikala_mirror

node.text:
Not only has it been a pleasure being blessed with the responsibility of carrying a child but I’m overjoyed that I’m doing it with my best friend @leeksneed . After losing my grandmother, this new blessing has been nothing short of amazing. After every storm there’s a rainbow 🌈👶🏽💙 New blessings, new adventures, new LIFE.  #Partyof3 #BoyMom 
🎥: @hiddenimagesdc
